flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    Gateway[API Gateway]
    Middleware[Rate Limit<br/>Middleware]
    Backend[Backend Services]
    Counter[("Shared Counter Store<br/>(in-memory cache)")]
    Config[Config Service]
    RuleCache[(Local Rule Cache)]

    Client -->|request| Gateway
    Gateway --> Middleware
    Middleware -->|allow| Backend
    Middleware -.->|429 + headers| Client
    Middleware <-->|atomic check+incr| Counter
    Middleware -->|lookup| RuleCache
    Config -.->|pub/sub invalidation| RuleCache

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class Gateway,Middleware,Backend service
    class Counter,RuleCache store
    class Config config
